race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Handicap
race.comment: DEVINE BELIEF (1) goes well fresh and maps for a beautiful run today. She was bold in the Bluff Knoll when fresh last campaign and while she comes here without a trial, she has plenty in her favour. Carries weight but deserves to and she can land the knockout blow first-up. BLACK ORA (10) has just missed in her past couple, flying late to miss by 0.5L in a tight finish. She drops in weight today and Pike remains in the saddle. Racing in strong order this time in work and can return to winning ways. JAZ SESSION (9) got the job done last start over this track and trip when beating Black Order. Drops in weight despite that victory and maps for a similar run this time around. Looks well placed to repeat the dose. RICHANCO (4) creates interest first-up on the back of a trial win. He's unbeaten fresh and while he's drawn wide, he can make his presence felt. DESERT WHISPER (3) was too good fresh and can build on that effort.
